	join sweet_potato_sasha [z_index="1"]
	sweet_potato_sasha: [color=CHARTREUSE]Freed from her bonds, Sasha wastes no time, redirecting the facility cameras.[/color] [color=YELLOW]People of Spud! This is Root Reserve! They've been feeding us to each other![/color] #id:13e
	leave sweet_potato_sasha

	[background arg="res://assets/narrative/escape_route.png" fade="2.0"]
	audio music "res://assets/music/narrative/sasha_theme_main.mp3" [fade="2.0" volume="-5.0" bus="Music"]
	join sweet_potato_sasha [z_index="1"]
	if {sasha_rescue_reaction} == "relieved":
		sweet_potato_sasha: [color=CHARTREUSE]Sasha takes your hand, intertwining her fingers with yours.[/color] You came back for me. Whatever happens next... we face it together. #id:s9e_015
	elif {sasha_rescue_reaction} == "angry":
		sweet_potato_sasha: [color=STEEL_BLUE]Sasha watches you carefully, seeing the fury still burning in your eyes.[/color] Channel that fire. We'll need it for what comes next. #id:s9e_016
	else:
		sweet_potato_sasha: [color=STEEL_BLUE]Sasha places a gentle hand on your shoulder.[/color] The guilt isn't yours to carry. You're here now. That's what matters. #id:s9e_017
	sweet_potato_sasha: [color=CHARTREUSE]We did it. The truth is out there now.[/color] We have a future to build! #id:13f
	leave sweet_potato_sasha